::Zardus::

Zardus steps back from the table, looking at the console as he hears Lady 
Hawk's question, a bit too preocupied for the word 'fail' to register.

"We are simply switching her internal systems. This bot seems to be more than 
just another soldier."

He puts Squizzy's old internal proccessor on the table, watching Squizzy for 
any sign of activity.
